{"tid":1320844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後針對白衫","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T13:39:53.000Z","uid":20028,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f33ceb08beee0d99f8a0b0150ff8811e00e1c992","tid":1320844,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:24:00.000Z","msg":"發夢有白衫狗同藍衫狗咬人 夢入面有人教<br />\n<br />\n共產黨最叻分化 視共產黨為學習榜樣<br />\n<br />\n由鬧狗開始做起 反正鬧狗都係發洩 我地要鬧得其所<br />\n例如: 屌你老母 唔關藍衫你地事 我地係屌白衫咋 推啲散仔出黎<br />\n<br />\n要圍既有機會都優先白衫狗<br />\n<br />\n我知好多隻藍衫狗都咬人 但係我地要為達目的不擇手段 暫時放低仇恨 令到最後一道防線瓦解"},{"pid":"3f9b958436a5e27ef683f6f43bcb0f0637d2e863","tid":1320844,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab935eb42df666b06ff8a1969ec77cd5a42e9b7d","tid":1320844,"uid":167506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"e5872a7a505d3bfdbaf8a18ad83892abc750e8bd","tid":1320844,"uid":1315,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">風向好似有d怪怪地 各位留意</span></span>"},{"pid":"e714c4c50a457037ae0762118929eba9e2f85bc2","tid":1320844,"uid":249721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持警察！支持監警會！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320279\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320279</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0632e0bf9b139b5f012ae624c578dc9886429042","tid":1320844,"uid":20028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5872a7a505d3bfdbaf8a18ad83892abc750e8bd","tid":1320844,"uid":1315,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:29